Package coms309.mainproject.schedule.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    Very similar to the Event class but holds information about Courses instead.
    Event
    This class stores all the data for an individual event in a compact way to make getting that data simple and easy
    EventEditor
    This class is entirely responsible for editing existing rows in the Events database.
    EventReader
    This class keeps the data for events shown in a Calendar Cell.
    EventWriter
    This class is entirely responsible for the creation of new events.
